"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: commands.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a &sheets; <link linkend=\"templates\">template</link> based on this "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Skapa en &sheets;-<link linkend=\"templates\">mall</link> baserat på det här "
"dokumentet."

